Mountain，is still the mountain
山，还是那座山
Cloud，is still the cloud
云，还是那朵云
You walk to the distance
你走向远方
carrying the distance farther than that
带着比远方更远的远
It is running cattle and sheep
是草原上奔跑的牛羊
Then the cloud falls down
白云坍塌了
You couldn't help weeping，being excited，and the tears reflect light.
你激动的泪倾泻不止，带着辉芒
like a raising sun
是初升的太阳
Tender glance is over there
温柔的眼神就会斜照过来
It is brilliant to my heart
在我心中放射出光明一闪
that is a lost rosy cloud at daybreak
是黎明迷失的霞光
At present，I must be burning the sky
此刻，我定当举火燎天
The footprints disordered by wind，line the grasses
草原，被风吹乱的足迹，成行
I'm going alone with myself
我只身前往
There is the field none has ever arrived
无人的领域
Cloud，is still the cloud
云，还是那朵云
Mountain，is still the mountain
山，还是那座山

注：旧作中译英，无韵自由体。另，可以尝试从末句向上读，文意也是通畅的。
